<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<%- include("partials/head", { title: "Our Story | FreezerMeals", description: "Meet the three teen founders behind FreezerMeals and their mission to make real food effortless." }) %>
<body>
    <%- include("partials/navbar") %>

    <main class="page">
        <section class="hero slim">
        <div>
            <div class="pill">Our story</div>
            <h1>Three teens. One mission: make real food effortless.</h1>
            <p class="tagline">FreezerMeals began with late-night study sessions and a shared frustration: great food shouldn’t take an hour to make. So we built a fresh-frozen kitchen to help everyone eat well on busy days.</p>
            <div style="margin-top: 20px; display:flex; gap:12px; flex-wrap:wrap;">
            <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/order">Start an order</a>
            <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="/how">How it works</a>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="hero-visual">
            <img src="https://placehold.co/640x360/jpg" alt="FreezerMeals founders together" />
            <div class="badge">Built in 2025</div>
        </div>
        </section>

        <section class="section">
        <div class="section-header">
            <h2>The spark</h2>
            <p class="section-lead">From school projects to a real kitchen. We tested recipes between exams, iterated on reheating guides, and asked friends to be our first tasters.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="grid cols-2">
            <div class="card">
            <h3>Why frozen?</h3>
            <p class="muted">Flash-freezing locks in flavor and nutrition without preservatives. It lets us cook in batches, reduce waste, and deliver consistently great meals you can reheat in minutes.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
            <h3>Why teens?</h3>
            <p class="muted">We grew up juggling school, sports, and part-time jobs. We wanted a way to keep eating real food without sacrificing time—or taste.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        </section>

        <section class="section">
        <div class="section-header">
            <h2>Meet the founders</h2>
            <p class="section-lead">Three friends, one shared kitchen, and a lot of taste tests.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="founders">
            <% for (let i = 0; i < data.founders.length; i++) { %>
                <div class="card founder">
                    <img src="<%= data.founders[i].image %>" alt="Founder portrait <%= data.founders[i].name %>" class="founder-image-2" />
                    <h3><%= data.founders[i].name %> — <%= data.founders[i].role %></h3>
                    <p class="muted"><%= data.founders[i].bio %></p>
                </div>
            <% } %>
