        </div>
        </section>

        <section class="section panel">
        <div class="cta">
            <div>
            <h2>What we believe</h2>
            <p class="section-lead">Food should be honest, easy, and joyful—even on your busiest days.</p>
            <ul class="muted" style="padding-left:18px; margin-top:0;">
                <li>Quality first: real ingredients, no shortcuts.</li>
                <li>Clarity: clear labels, reheating tips, and allergen callouts.</li>
                <li>Convenience: freezer-stable meals that taste like today.</li>
            </ul>
            <div style="display:flex; gap:12px; flex-wrap:wrap; margin-top:12px;">
                <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/order">Build my box</a>
                <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="/reviews">See customer stories</a>
            </div>
            </div>
            <div>
            <img src="https://placehold.co/520x320/jpg" alt="Team cooking together" style="width:100%; border-radius: var(--radius); border:1px solid var(--border); box-shadow: var(--shadow);" />
            </div>
        </div>
        </section>

        <section class="section">
        <div class="section-header">
            <h2>Milestones</h2>
            <p class="section-lead">From a home kitchen to delivering across town.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="grid cols-3">
            <div class="card">
            <h3>Week 1</h3>
            <p class="muted">First 20 meals sold to friends and family. Lots of feedback, lots of tweaking.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
            <h3>Week 3</h3>
            <p class="muted">Flash-freeze process dialed in. New labels with heating and allergen details.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
            <h3>Week 6</h3>
            <p class="muted">Local delivery routes set. Family bundles launch—instant favorite.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        </section>

        <section class="section panel">
        <div class="cta">
            <div>
            <h2>Join the journey</h2>
            <p class="section-lead">Tell us what you want in your freezer. We’ll keep building menus around how you actually live.</p>
            <div style="display:flex; gap:12px; flex-wrap:wrap;">
                <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/order">Start an order</a>
                <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="/contact">Talk to us</a>
                <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="/newsletter">Get updates</a>
            </div>
            </div>
            <div>
            <img src="https://placehold.co/520x320/png" alt="FreezerMeals box" style="width:100%; border-radius: var(--radius); border:1px solid var(--border); box-shadow: var(--shadow);" />
            </div>
        </div>
        </section>
